      "estimatedTime": 20,
      "content": {
        "text": "Now that you understand the basics of Hangul, let's explore all the vowels and consonants in detail.\n\nKorean has 14 basic consonants and 10 basic vowels. There are also compound vowels and double consonants that we'll cover in later lessons.\n\nEach character has a specific shape and sound, and understanding these will help you read Korean words.",
